getPresaleRemainTime().details: Get the remaining time until the end of pre-staking period

lookupPreStake(uint256,uint256).details: Shows the possibility of pre-staking a certain amount of tokens and the BNB required for it..

params.lockPeriod: Period of time of releasing locked LP tokens.

returns._0: Amount of BNB proper to adding liquidity token.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

requestPreStake(uint256,uint256).details: Accept request of pre-stake and add liquidity.

params.lockPeriod: Period of time of releasing locked LP tokens.

params._discountRate: Indicates what percentage of the expected publication price will be set as the discount price
params._lifetime: pre-staking duratation, on ellapsed this time, token will be published
params._publishPriceDenominator: discount price of pre-staking tokens to set.(denominator)
params._publishPriceNumerator: discount price of pre-staking tokens to set.(numerator)
params.cap: max amount of tokens that can be presaled.
params.lockMin: investors can lock only more than this period.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdrawAll(address).details: Change the owner of MetaAx token to another

withdrawLP().details: Investor will actually be the onwer of LP tokens.
